I just wanted to make a post to thank all my clients and @wealthystreettattoo for helping me live my dream. Taking time away from doing my favorite thing is hard for me, tattooing is apart of my identity and I’ve worked so hard to do tattoos that I’m proud of. That being said I’m so fortunate to be able to take time off to spend time with my baby and to try to be the mom I want to be. I’m so thankful to all my friends that have shown up to be a great support system for my family, the generosity has been huge. I feel blessed 😇

Going to start accepting  some tattoos starting next week. Private studio. A few rules for now- friends/ female clients only. Flash only/ no custom designs. Hand size or smaller. No friends. No touch up appointments! I will be back to normal tattooing a few days a week this fall. DM for appointments. $50 dollar deposit. $100 minimum.
